headline: Is Visa Stock a Millionaire-Maker?
summary: Visa (NYSE: V) certainly falls into this category, as its shares have produced a total return of 2,560% since their initial public offering in 2008 (as of March 13).  One reason that Visa is a fantastic business is because its competitive position is virtually unassailable.  With $4.1 trillion in total payment volume in the last three months of calendar 2024, it has top market share by far in the U.S. with this key metric.
